    "affected_lt": "13.1.10",
    "fixed_version": "13.1.10"
  },
  "analyst_note": "GitLab version exposed via /api/v4/version JSON endpoint (may require auth on newer instances). Fixed: 13.1.10. CVEs: CVE-2020-13311.",
